page.title: 06MY DIARY
page.content: I got up at 8.oo. I had my breakfast at 8.15.I washed and dressed at 8.30. I went to violin practice at 8.55. It finished at 9.45.When I got home I had a cup of tea.At 10.15 we went to town to do some shopping.We came back at 11.00.I went to my bedroom and I read a book called The Case of the Missing Masterpiece.My mum called me at 12.15 for my dinner.I had a cup of soup,a piece of bread and a cup of tea.After dinner we went to my mum's friends house.I played with Vanessa until 4.00.When we got home I played hop scotch until 4.30.I went to my bedroom to finish my book.At 5.00 I had my tea. For tea I had a baked potato and a cup of tea.I watched televison until 8.30 when I went to bed.
